{
  "stem": "7546.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My sister committed suicide the day she arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sara, the oldest, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was 18 years older than  me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the age of 38, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she looked beautiful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In Auschwitz, I was put into a block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people were lucky-- they went into blocks, barracks that had wood where you could sleep, under first, or second, or third.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My barrack was not finished yet, so we slept on the hard floor-- cold, hard floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I remember everything-- yeah, I remember it very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went in a very large field when we arrived, and we were finally picked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went into a very large field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stood in that field, and a prisoner-- a Jewish prisoner-- came up and he stood on a small platform and gave us a speech.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dear Jews, you came here in a camp, and you'll live.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You'll only live if you give anything that you have hidden in your body.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we know-- and it's true, people had hidden things in their body, whether it was a ring, a diamond, a watch, or money, or gold pieces.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the anus, or in the mouth, or if you swallowed something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If the Germans will find it, if the German will know that you have something, you're shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You better give everything out now, because you're going to shower, and you're going to get a uniform, and you look like everyone else here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But give all your possessions up right now, and that will save your life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whoever wanted, gave everything up.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
